🍕Pizza or Ice Cream? 🍦
🏈NFL or Soccer? ⚽
👀Logan Paul or Jake Paul?
Think you know @kingryan? Think again... 🤯
We're catching up with Ryan Garcia to find out what really matters ahead of the biggest test of his career to date...
Ryan Garcia vs. Luke Campbell. 2nd January. 
The fight is on 🥊🔥
#Gymshark

node.text:
🔥 #Gymshark66 2021 is coming 🔥
Want to join in? 🙌
1. Decide on your 66-day pledge between now and 23:59 GMT on 31st December 📝
2. Show us your progress during the 66-day challenge between 1st January and 7th March 🗓
3. Be in with the chance to win super prizes, such as an EXCLUSIVE GYMSHARK EXPERIENCE 😱
4. Join in on weekly challenges for the chance to win limited edition Gymshark goodies 🦈
Got a question? Drop 'em below and we'll get back to ya 💪
For more information and T+Cs, head to the link in our bio 💻
#Gymshark

node.text:
Deload Sidekick @drmikethe2nd chats all things mental wellbeing and self-care during these tough times. 

World Mental Health Day with Dr Mike Banna intends to create positive, impactful change through conversation. The views and opinions expressed by the speaker within the IGTV are based on their own personal experiences. They do not reflect the views or opinions of Gymshark, nor do they provide medical advice. 
Have any further questions for Dr Mike? Let us know below ↓ 
#Gymshark

node.title: World Mental Health Day with Dr Mike Banna

node.text:
Last week @aimee_cringle won the European Championships 👏

"Winning this means everything to me. It really justifies my decision to become a full-time athlete earlier this year and focus on CrossFit 100%. I know there's still a lot of work to do to achieve the goals I have set myself, but I love competing and I love the community at the competitions; everyone is so encouraging and supportive! Now it's time to work on my weaknesses ready for the next competition.

My coach knows my strengths and weaknesses and he understands not only how to programme for me, but also how to keep my mentality on track and taught me how to believe in myself and trust the process."
#Gymshark

node.text:
Strength is...
Getting up on the days you don't want to.
Pushing through when you think you can't.
Trying even when you've failed many times.
Being told you can't, but proving them wrong.
How do you define strength? 💪
📸: @big_z_2020, @deniceemoberg, @noah_mbuyamba, @toningtoni, @joefraser1, @leaschreiner__, @kingryan, @devonlevesque 
#Gymshark

@nochtlii stands next to glass doors in front of a white wall with one hand on her hip and the other holding the Whitney V3 Straw Bottle while wearing the V3 Sports bra in goal blue and leggings in pollen.

@angieberbuer sits on a wooden bench, looking across to her right while wearing the Whitney V3 crop tank in eucalyptus and shorts in goal blue. She also wears the V3 robe in unbleached and has the Straw bottle to her right.

@georgiaarichardss stands posed in front of a white wall with cacti, smiling to her left with one hand holding the Whitney V3 straw bottle while wearing the V3 crop tank and leggings set in eucalyptus.
@tarasbody is seen doing a side lunge while wearing the Whitney V3 sports bra in unbleached and cycling shorts in eucalyptus.
